Package: didbjs
Title: Borusyak-Jaravel-Spiess Difference-in-Differences Imputation for R
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: person("Aniket", "Panjwani", email = "aniket@aieconomist.io", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Borusyak-Jaravel-Spiess difference-in-differences
    imputation estimator, event-study plotting helpers, and compatibility
    wrappers for common Stata, Python, and R workflows. The package ships with
    smoke fixtures and keeps a larger parity suite in the source repository for
    reproducible reference validation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/aniketpanjwani/didbjs
BugReports: https://github.com/aniketpanjwani/didbjs/issues
